data.description: This North facing home is situated at the top of Beckton Ave with views of the Basin. As you enter into this 2,574 sq ft two level home you will find 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, space for an office, and plenty of room for entertaining or housing guests. There is a large room tucked downstairs perfect for a game hall, media room, or second living room. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar and a formal dining room ideal for your holiday traditions. A sliding glass door exits onto a spacious deck overlooking a second patio and the large backyard. There is ample room for parking when hosting your evening BBQ's, a pad for your RV, or space for your hobbyist with too many toys.We have an appraisal which can be transferred to any lender and a pest and dry rot inspection on file.
